{"tid":1624820,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"三年前你地鞭撻梁天琦，正如今日你地鞭撻臨時政府","createTime":"2019-10-05T04:57:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T01:32:32.000Z","uid":35699,"like":32,"dislike":85,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"e927efce1d78ebea9f61c908abceb71a7752453e","tid":1624820,"uid":35699,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:57:16.000Z","msg":"暴力升級，打壓升級<br />\n反彈都會升級<br />\n<br />\n係得香港比人瘋狂射爆眼都仲係原地踏步<br />\n左顧右盼，一味將自己責任外判<br />\n<br />\n你地贏左啦，我就等美國，等輸<br />\n等所有前線手足斷送一生<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n無底線抗爭係理念，唔係口號<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地將會送更多手足去死<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/D44NjVn.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FD44NjVn.jpg&h=5b966ad5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8319b611b11d8d0164ccb5b4ec77709ba2890db3","tid":1624820,"uid":257293,"like":2,"dislike":6,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:57:41.000Z","msg":"其實裝修有好多種<br />\n點解唔裝修成連儂牆？<br />\n新聞出嘅圖可以贏到輿論同國際支持<br />\n又可以target警世呢啲紅底中資<br />\n佢哋要拆要清都要搞到一大輪<br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/fr/cp0/e15/q65/24852222_1729358367084760_1911336044043144089_n.jpg?_nc_cat=102&amp;efg=eyJpIjoidCJ9&amp;_nc_oc=AQkIOjsel3Yjc1B7cRnhIfagIvmR4f4aVTBnzK5PhcCs6SwzlwstlaxQaqELvb708RI&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg10-1.fna&amp;oh=6ff3cb4718a8dad53be9276dd33cad72&amp;oe=5E364A79\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg10-1.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2Ffr%2Fcp0%2Fe15%2Fq65%2F24852222_1729358367084760_1911336044043144089_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D102%26efg%3DeyJpIjoidCJ9%26_nc_oc%3DAQkIOjsel3Yjc1B7cRnhIfagIvmR4f4aVTBnzK5PhcCs6SwzlwstlaxQaqELvb708RI%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg10-1.fna%26oh%3D6ff3cb4718a8dad53be9276dd33cad72%26oe%3D5E364A79&h=7003ea3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n裝修 + 文宣 可以同時做<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1624381\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1624381</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"68cfe2d0811cd92c732f2c45a11c34216bcd282f","tid":1624820,"uid":310765,